  • public class FilteredThreeAxisJoystick
extends ThreeAxisJoystick
    Implements a Joystick that filters all of its axis values through a given JoystickFilterSet.

      • FilteredThreeAxisJoystick

        public FilteredThreeAxisJoystick(int port,
                                 JoystickFilterSet filters)
        Constructs a new FilteredJoystick that will send the axis values of the joystick on the given port through the given JoystickFilterSet.
        Parameters:
        port - The port of the joystick that is to be wrapped by this FilteredJoystick.
        filters - The JoystickFilterSet through which all axis values are to be sent.
